MARC LEISHMAN:   I was leading after one round last year, and wasn't after four.   I'd rather be leading after four this year.   I felt a bit of pressure last year.   Obviously leading you don't want to do anything stupid.   I don't want to do anything stupid tomorrow.   I'm moving forward.   
   
  
  
  
  
  

